            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#很多人发现肿瘤时已经是中晚期# 】网传#吃银耳能抗肿瘤# 真的吗？[疑问]专家表示，银耳含有银耳多糖，是真正的功能活性物质，它可以调节细胞免疫、体液...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%97%B6%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%97%B6%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#很多人发现肿瘤时已经是中晚期#</span></a> 】网传<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E9%93%B6%E8%80%B3%E8%83%BD%E6%8A%97%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E9%93%B6%E8%80%B3%E8%83%BD%E6%8A%97%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃银耳能抗肿瘤#</span></a> 真的吗？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>专家表示，银耳含有银耳多糖，是真正的功能活性物质，它可以调节细胞免疫、体液免疫，从而提高人体免疫功能，通过增强免疫力可以诱导肿瘤细胞的凋亡，起到抗肿瘤的功效👇🏻（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4954923347935267" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hioy7m0b11j21hc0u0diz.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/83gmzOTvlx089eM4MCCI010412005wYM0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696885940&amp;ssig=65E63bDO3L&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3Kjh59Ghlx089eM4IUfe010412002OPZ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696885940&amp;ssig=0fWHAsp6Hb&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/QrUNNQYolx089eM4rQ2I010412001M3z0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696885940&amp;ssig=aly2CpXZ4%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4954923347935267" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
